*.pyc

# --- LaTeX build artifacts ---
docs/*.aux
docs/*.log
docs/*.toc
docs/*.out
docs/*.synctex.gz
docs/chapters/*.aux

# --- Original raw screenshots (renamed copies are versioned) ---
docs/img/Screenshot*.jpeg
docs/img/Screenshot*.png

# --- OS ---
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
frontend/package.json.md5

# --- Local tooling / build dir ---
.claude/
/build/
